The '''Endeavor Award''' is an award celebrating the contributions on the public benefit of flying.<ref>{{cite journal|magazine=AOPA Pilot|title=Endeavor Awards back for second year|page=26|date=March 2015|author=Julie Summers Walker}}</ref>
The award was established in 2014 by producer and pilot Mark Wolper. The presenter's at the [[California Science Center]] for 2015 are [[Ben Affleck]] and Scott Terry.
